23:48.000Z","msg":"香港果面cut, 對面海關,公安,月台清潔人手照舊<br />\n還掂營運成本幾多都要硬, 理撚得你客量係0<br />\n我照擺人你就要比一地兩檢人工各樣成本<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6d5c1b2d875822687653b5118ab13efaa2f6110","tid":1076250,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T18:07:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7imzKiC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7imzKiC.png&h=f4a6eb33&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"46f5d98100ddc5006feae6044ea953a71007adac","tid":1076250,"uid":33821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a5be1105659165afdd6ab753eb832b6edd7f7a2","tid":1076250,"uid":80080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T17:05:00.000Z","msg":"口講60 明明走200"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T03:02:36.000Z","msg":"淨低個140係第2波到啊?"}]}